p=int(input('enter principal amount'))
t=int(input('enter time period'))
r=int(input('enter rate of interest'))
si=p*t*r/100
print('SIMPLE INTEREST:',si)
emi=(p+si)/(t*12)
print('EMI',emi)


Output:
enter principal amount120000
enter time period2
enter rate of interest12000
SIMPLE INTEREST: 28800000.0
EMI 1205000.0
